Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:47.19,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I made it a little strong,\Nbecause you seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:52.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You read me like\Na book. It’s delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m glad I didn’t\Nbring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:06.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It gives me an excuse\Nto stay a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:10.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:46.93,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:57.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is there a special\Nguest coming tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,A certain someone from the past is coming with the owner and his wife tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:03.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:08.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, what is “Teo’s Specially-made Dolce Piatto” exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:16.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, he’s not much for\NTeo’s dolce, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, it’s been\Na while, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ve been\Nexpecting you, Marzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The owner and his wife\Nhaven’t arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You all look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.74,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I hear about the restaurant\Nhere and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:41.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Have you lost weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That’s because Gigi and I used to eat a ton, back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Speaking of Gigi…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He hasn’t changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Eating as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.67,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Gigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:10.43,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn’t that one of the\Nreally expensive bottles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.89,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:28.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I promised not\Nto leave the kitchen…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.74,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Today’s a special occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Come on, introduce yourself\Nto your predecessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It’s a pleasure to\Nmeet you. I’m Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:47.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m Marzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Looks like you’ve hired another cute, young lady again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He used to help\Nin the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Besides Gigi, he’s been in the business longer than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Dell’orso has quite the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:08.28,Ristorante signs franklin gothic medium,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\pos(438,339)\c&HEBEBEA&\3c&H3C3E42&\be1\fad(945,973)}4 years prior
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You overworked yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.58,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Should I call your folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:21.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,After you’re discharged tomorrow,\Nwant to stop for a drink on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You know, at the\Nbar where he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:30.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah… okay. Let’s do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:35.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m feeling better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Where’s that man?\NThat older barista.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, my brother-in-law? He hasn’t worked here since last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.30,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What? He quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ah, I get it. That’s why you came along to get me, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:14.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And wearing a suit\Non your day off…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:21.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I used to spend my days, waiting for work to get out, so I could go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,There are plenty of\Ngentlemen in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but a place where you can have a drink and truly be at ease is rare indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Would that be strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There’s still that\Ncameriere left…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What about the barista\Nfrom that bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:54.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yeah, I had the same thought,\Nso I got his name and phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.06,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano De Luca…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.02,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m afraid I’ll have to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I just grew tired of working\Nas a barista, so I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I don’t think I can go back\Nto working the late shift…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:18.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Quit? Didn’t you just use your sick days to spend some time with your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But still, it’s a\Ngreat opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You’re more suited to being\Na cameriere than a barista, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There are plenty of young men who can be camerieres.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Why would you want\Nsomeone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,To be honest,\Nit’s for my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,For your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:50.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She’s got what you’d\Ncall peculiar tastes…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ve been planning on opening the ristorante for months,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:08:00.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but she collapsed the\Nother day, from overworking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, I’d like to do\Nsomething for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll introduce you\Nto someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just accept that\Nand go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He’s a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:18.43,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How can I put it…\NA real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ve been working at\Na ristorante outside of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ve been there\Nabout twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Twenty years, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:35.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The owner there has\Nbeen very generous to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but he passed\Naway recently…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:41.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The new owner doesn’t\Ntake as kindly to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:46.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m sure he knows\Nwhat I’m referring to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:10.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I heard you used to\Nwork together…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He’s a brilliant man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He’s incredibly sophisticated…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:20.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But, he had to quit\Nwhen his wife got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:27.12,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, I’m sure he’ll sympathize with the emotions you have towards your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’d love for him\Nto work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:38.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Say no more.\NI’ll convince him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.14,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NBut, what about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:45.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’d like to mull it\Nover a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ve worked at the same\Nplace for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We convinced each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Some Orsini wine\Nwas involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.37,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,However, there’s that\Nsign out back…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Seeking bespectacled men,\Nfifty or older…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.43,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just saw this, guys.\NWhat do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:27.23,Ristorante,,0,0,0,,Forgive my attire.\NI was out for a jog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Let me get my spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ve got no experience\Nas a cameriere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but I’ve worked\Nplenty of different jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,As a concierge in a hotel, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’d love to try and\Nwork as a cameriere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He looks like a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:54.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce you all once again. This is an old associate of mine, Marzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:11:00.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He used to help out in the kitchen sometimes, when I ran the restaurant next to the winery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,These are the chefs,\NVanna and Dario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:05.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They’re both masters\Nin the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio, a cameriere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Also, Luciano and Vito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,These are the gentlemen who will manage the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They’re all old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,And this is Gigi,\Nour sommelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is the wine list.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is the food menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:29.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’ll switch it up seasonly,\Nbut we’ll start with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:44.14,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, right.\NThey all wear spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It’s no big deal.\NDon’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.50,Ristorante italic,MV,0,0,0,,I hope this puts\Na smile on her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:28.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The owner and his wife\Nsure are late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He told me to get\Nhere before it opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m hungry, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just a little longer, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:44.99,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I’m sure {\i0}she’s{\i1} still\Nat work… My goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.12,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll take your coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.50,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How about you bring out a little\Nof the food they make for the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.51,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ll move you to your table when the owner and his wife show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:14.52,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, keep them\Ncompany in their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.89,Ristorante,,0,0,0,,Huh? But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.06,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll let the kitchen\Nstaff know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:25.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The dinner service\Nwon’t hit its peak for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Also, part of your job is to learn the restaurant’s history.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:30.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.79,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Twenty years already…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.59,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,That’s so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.63,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I’ve got to work\Nmy hardest, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.93,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,There’s so much about\NClaudio I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:57.14,Ristorante signs franklin gothic medium,,0,0,0,,{\fs42\pos(438,339)\c&HEBEBEA&\3c&H3C3E42&\be1\fad(945,0)}4 years prior
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:02.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Being invited in before it even opens… I’m so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I wonder what the\Nristorante will be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:09.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I made special reservations. Let’s just take our time and enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Bear Street…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.43,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:38.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ristorante casetta dell’orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Madam, will it be\Nto your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I won’t pull any punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,B-Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:10.18,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Allow me to take your shawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.06,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It’s beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Want to relax a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.01,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Order anything\Non the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I wonder what\NI should get…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Here is the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:06.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ve prepared a special menu to pair with the Orsini wine that you like so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I’m delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.20,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What does that entail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, it includes\Nseasonal mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:24.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ll be serving porcini\Nmushrooms tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.29,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,H-He’s a complete gentleman…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.55,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,And he’s wearing spectacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Eggplant is in season now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:36.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’ll be including it\Nin tonight’s antipasto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I cannot fathom another\Nrestaurant this wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Both the food and\Nwine are delectable,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and so is the scenery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You know, I’d like\Nto meet the chef, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:03.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure she won’t mind the fact that I’m not a gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It’s fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m just the sous-chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.05,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Dario?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.97,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone who works\Nhere is older!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.30,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That’s wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:24.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll revisit this situation\Nwhen I’m an older man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,More than anything else…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:48.54,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The fact that you thought of me this much makes me so happy, Lorenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.51,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It was a splendid evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:14.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wow, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.28,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, I see you told her\Nabout that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,When I saw the two\Nof them that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I just knew.
Comment: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:34.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:38.68,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I knew I’d love this place\Nfor a long time to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:45.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This restaurant’s origins go back to the owner’s deep love for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Be that as it may,\Nthey sure are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I got here as\Nquickly as I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It appears he’s arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry to\Nkeep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.29,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Olga wanted to\Ngive this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She couldn’t break away\Nfrom work. I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I’ll catch her\Nnext time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Come on, let me buy\Nyou a drink, Lorenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure. That’s a fantastic idea.
Comment: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Okay, how about…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She is such a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You planning on taking\Nthe whole night off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:32.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was just on my way\Nback to the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:34.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:38.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I will! I’ll work\Nfor twenty years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You worked late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:04.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was so hectic today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:07.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Let’s invite Marzio out\Nthe next chance we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:12.19,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We can have him join us at the end of the day, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:17.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Seeing you smile\Ncleanses my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Grazie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.96,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We’re not involved\Nin their feud,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,so let’s stay on\Ngood terms, Gigi.